'''Kelfin''' ({{lang-en|Kelvin}}; {{lang-ar|كلفن}}) waa [[halbeeg]] lagu [[xisaab]]iyo [[heerkul]]ka. 
Ereyga ''Kelfin'' waxaa loogu magac daray [[Saynis|Injineer]] reer England Baron Kelvin (1824–1904) kaas oo sameeyay ''Halbeeg'' cabir dhamaystiran<ref name=res413>{{cite web |title=Resolution 4: Definition of the SI unit of thermodynamic temperature (kelvin) |work=Resolutions of the 13th CGPM |url=http://www.bipm.fr/en/CGPM/db/13/4/ |publisher=Bureau International des Poids et Mesures |year=1967 |accessdate=2008-02-06}}</ref>. 

Halbeegan waxaa loo soo gaabiyaa '''K''' (Kelfin). 

Qiyaasta halbeegan jabjab ahaan waa 1/273.16<ref name=sib211>{{cite web |title=Rules and style conventions for expressing values of quantities |work=SI Brochure, 8th edition |pages=Section 2.1.1.5 |url=http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/chapter2/2-1/kelvin.html |publisher=Bureau International des Poids et Mesures |year=1967 |accessdate=2012-08-27}}</ref>). Cabirkan oo inta badan lagu qiyaaso [[Kul|kuleylka iyo qaboowga]] ayaa wuxuu lambar todoba ka yahay '''Halbeegyada Caalamiga ah''' ee [[duni]]da. 

Marka halbeega Kelfin loo bedelaayo [[Salsiyas]] waa +273.16.

Tusaale ahaan haddii heerkulka maanta yahay 30&nbsp;°C markaad Kelfin u bedelayso waa +273.16 taas oo u dhiganta 303.16 K. 

